{"type":null,"faqId":12922,"title":"P7 WLAN 连接失败，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点为加密热点，请输入正确密码，注意区分大小写。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请确认</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点名称或密码是否发生了变更，重新搜索要连接的热点，输入正确的密码后连接。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请将手机置于</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点的有效距离内，距离太远会使网络信号变弱，导致网络连接自动断开。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span>WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点可能已达到最大连接数，请尝试连接其他的可用网络。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若连接</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点时一直显示正在获取</span><span> IP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">地址，请按照以下操作设置静态</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span>IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若是加密热点，在</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置界面，点击要连接的热点名称。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在弹出的对话框勾选“显示高级选项”，在“</span><span>IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置”区域点击下拉菜单，选择“静态”，手动输入</span><span> IP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">地址和域名等信息。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>输入密码，然后点击“连接”。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=35382\" /> \n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若是开放热点，在</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置界面，长按要连接的热点名称。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在弹出的选项菜单中，点击“修改网络”。在弹出的对话框中，勾选“显示高级选项”，在“</span><span>IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置”区域点击下拉菜单，选择“静态”，手动输入</span><span> IP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">地址和域名等信息后保存。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接成功后，状态栏会显示</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图标。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=35383\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">某些公共</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点可能需要在网页端登录连接，详情请咨询</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点提供商。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若问题依然存在，请重新打开</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开关或重启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":2,"unUseful":15,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3823","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1400141844000,"seriesProductName":"Sophia-L00,Sophia-L05,Sophia-L07,Sophia-L09","visitedTimes":1358,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":15,"times":5,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"4","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"P7  WLAN","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}